title: Michael Kors Watch Hunger Stop PSA (Global)
description:
Join Michael Kors and the United Nations World Food Programme in the fight to end "the world's most solvable problem." Share the video with your friends and family, join the movement and Watch Hunger Stop.

To donate, visit WFP.org/KORS.

#WatchHungerStop
